WEBVTT

00:00:01.233 --> 00:00:03.600
(announcer)
Previously on "Yu‐Gi‐Oh!
ARC‐V"...

00:00:03.600 --> 00:00:06.933
It's time for today's
third mega match up!

00:00:06.933 --> 00:00:09.300
It's You Show School's
Sora Perse

00:00:09.300 --> 00:00:13.066
versus Leo Institute's
Shay Obsidian!

00:00:13.066 --> 00:00:15.866
I can't believe Shay's dueling
for the Leo Institute

00:00:15.866 --> 00:00:17.933
after all the drama
he had with Julia.

00:00:17.933 --> 00:00:20.233
Shay was the one who
attacked Julia's professor

00:00:20.233 --> 00:00:22.233
and all those LID students.

00:00:22.233 --> 00:00:24.400
Something weird's
definitely going on here.

00:00:25.866 --> 00:00:29.133
Fusion Summoners like you
deserve no mercy.

00:00:29.133 --> 00:00:31.833
And none will be shown!

00:00:31.833 --> 00:00:33.033
(both)
Let's duel!

00:00:33.033 --> 00:00:34.600
Let's make this
the funnest show

00:00:34.600 --> 00:00:36.700
anybody here's
ever seen!

00:00:36.700 --> 00:00:38.733
The days of dueling for fun

00:00:38.733 --> 00:00:41.466
no longer exist for me
and my friends.

00:00:41.466 --> 00:00:44.600
Dueling is about survival.
Huh?

00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:46.500
The joy and happiness,

00:00:46.500 --> 00:00:48.866
it was all taken away
that day.

00:00:48.866 --> 00:00:52.100
They just showed up,
they wrecked our city.

00:00:52.100 --> 00:00:55.200
The enemy took
everything away from us.

00:00:55.200 --> 00:00:57.633
What city?
Who was this enemy?!

00:00:57.633 --> 00:01:00.433
Countless were taken
on that dark day.

00:01:00.433 --> 00:01:02.733
I Xyz Summon!

00:01:02.733 --> 00:01:07.166
Witness the assent of
Raidraptor Rise Falcon!

00:01:10.500 --> 00:01:12.933
Attack with
Ravaging Rebellion!

00:01:12.933 --> 00:01:15.833
Ahh!

00:01:15.833 --> 00:01:17.966
(Nico)
Unbelievable!

00:01:17.966 --> 00:01:21.800
Will Sora be able to stand up
to this aerial onslaught?

00:01:23.233 --> 00:01:26.100
You better get ready
for some plot twists.

00:01:26.100 --> 00:01:29.933
And I'm sure you won't
like the ending!

